'''Hortus Haren''' is a [[botanical garden]] of in [[Haren, Groningen]], [[Netherlands]]. First created in 1642,<ref>{{cite book | title = International Directory of Botanical Gardens | first = Vernon Hilton | last = Heywood | authorlink = Vernon Hilton Heywood | publisher = Koeltz Scientific Books | year = 1990 | page = 477 | isbn = 9783874293198 | url = https://books.google.com/books?id=iNTiAAAAMAAJ}}</ref> it is the largest botanical garden in the country.<ref>{{cite book | title = Gardens of Europe: A Traveller's Guide | first = Charles | last = Quest-Ritson | publisher = Antique Collectors Club | year = 2007 | page = 282 | isbn = 9781870673556 | url = https://books.google.com/books?id=yCtLAQAAIAAJ}}</ref>

